t%20said%20the%20authorities%20have%20received%2014%2C000%20comments%20on%20the%20new%20rules%20and%20have%20decided%20to%20amend%20the%20regulations.%20The%20court%20disposed%20of%20the%20PIL%20after%20setting%20a%20three-month%20deadline%20for%20the%20Centre.%20The%20PIL%20had%20sought%20directions%20to%20the%20Centre%20and%20states%20to%20make%20the%20Front%20of%20Package%20Warning%20Label%20mandatory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202024%2C%20the%20FSSAI%20approved%20a%20proposal%20to%20display%20nutritional%20information%2C%20including%20total%20sugar%2C%20salt%20and%20saturated%20fat%20in%20bold%20letters%20and%20prominent%20font%20size%20on%20labels%20of%20packaged%20food%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20amendment%2C%20a%20government%20statement%20said%2C%20is%20aimed%20at%20empowering%20consumers%20to%20better%20understand%20the%20nutritional%20value%20of%20the%20product%20they%20are%20consuming.%20Following%20this%2C%20the%20draft%20notification%20was%20put%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20for%20suggestions%20and%20objections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20information%20regarding%20per%20serve%20percentage%20(%25)%20contribution%20to%20Recommended%20Dietary%20Allowances%20(RDAs)%20would%20be%20given%20in%20bold%20letters%20for%20total%20sugar%2C%20total%20saturated%20fat%20and%20sodium%20content.%20Regulation%202%20(v)%20and%205(3)%20of%20FSS%20(Labelling%20and%20Display)%20Regulation%2C%202020%20specifies%20requirements%20to%20mention%20serving%20size%20and%20nutritional%20information%20on%20the%20food%20product%20label%2C%20respectively%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20government%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlong%20with%20empowering%20consumers%20make%20healthier%20choices%2C%20the%20amendment%20would%20also%20contribute%20towards%20efforts%20to%20combat%20the%20rise%20of%20Non-Communicable%20Diseases%20(NCDs)%20and%20promote%20public%20health%20and%20well-being.%20The%20prioritisation%20of%20the%20development%20of%20clear%20and%20distinguish%20labelling%20requirements%20would%20help%20in%20the%20global%20effort%20to%20combat%20NCDs%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744195080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4qgfvaco_supreme-court-new_625x300_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-fssai-you-have-grandchildren-top-courts-deadline-for-packaged-food-labels-8124401%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20set%20a%20three-month%20deadline%20for%20the%20Centre%20to%20implement%20food%20safety%20norms%20that%20make%20it%20mandatory%20to%20display%20key%20information%20about%20packaged%20food%20items%20on%20containers.%20Hearing%20a%20Public%20Interest%20Litigation%2C%20the%20bench%20of%20Justice%20JB%20Pa%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ather%20Energy%20cuts%20IPO%20size%20by%2025%25%20to%20%E2%82%B93%2C000%20crore%2C%20delays%20launch%20to%20May%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744194762000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fipo%2Father-trims-ipo-size-by-25-per-cent-to-rs-3-000-crore-to-launch-in-may-125040900725_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ather%20goes%20ahead%20with%20IPO%20despite%20global%20volatility%20and%20market%20slump%20triggered%20by%20Trump's%20tariff%20shock%3B%20valuation%20also%20revised%20downward%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fipo%2Father-trims-ipo-size-by-25-per-cent-to-rs-3-000-crore-to-launch-in-may-125040900725_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jaya%20Bachchan%20calls%20Abhishek%20and%20Shweta%20her%20greatest%20achievement%20-%20Exclusive%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744194751000%2C%22visual%