h%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20do%20drop-offs%20and%20pick-ups%2C%20and%20I%20can%20go%20to%20all%20of%20her%20Girl%20Scout%20outings%20and%20volunteer%20at%20her%20school.%20Lately%2C%20I%20have%20started%20to%20work%20on%20my%20freelance%20PR%20business%20and%20have%20been%20writing%20more%2C%20and%20it%20feels%20good%20to%20be%20able%20to%20work%20in%20a%20way%20that%20allows%20me%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-stay-at-home-dad-quit-dream-job-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espend%20more%20time%20with%20my%20daughter%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20I%20have%20the%20privilege%20of%20a%20flexible%20schedule%2C%20younger%20parents%20have%20the%20upper%20hand%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20fun%20stuff.%20Playing%20with%20my%20daughter%20and%20her%20friends%20is%20hard%20on%20the%20body%20when%20you're%20over%2040%3B%20your%20back%20aches%2C%20your%20knees%20hurt%2C%20and%20you%20feel%20tired%20much%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20in%20what%20elder%20Latinas%20call%20my%20%26quot%3Bse%C3%B1ora%20era%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20means%20I%20am%20slowing%20down%20physically%20and%20have%20to%20focus%20more%20on%20recharging%2C%20which%20younger%20parents%20don't%20really%20need.%20My%20fitness%20routine%20isn't%20about%20vanity%20anymore%20%E2%80%94%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20stay%20active%20and%20watch%20what%20we%20eat%20so%20we%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folder-mom-40s-stop-taking-health-for-granted-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estay%20healthy%20for%20our%20daughter%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20keep%20up%20with%20her%20as%20she%20grows%20without%20falling%20apart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20camp%20twice%20a%20year%20and%20go%20to%20the%20beach%20and%20museums%20so%20that%20she%20is%20never%20bored.%20I%20know%20that%20some%20younger%20parents%20are%20more%20vibrant%20and%20fun%2C%20like%20my%20parents%20when%20I%20was%20growing%20up.%20When%20she's%20a%20teenager%2C%20we'll%20be%