20been%20prompting%20the%20Grok%20account%20to%20use%20racial%20slurs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ExAI%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-ceo-elon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk's%3C%2Fa%3E%20artificial%20intelligence%20startup%2C%20is%20hiring%20for%20several%20safety%20roles%20amid%20new%20feature%20releases%20for%20Grok%2C%20including%20an%20%26quot%3BNSFW%26quot%3B%20version%20and%20a%20tool%20that%20has%20been%20used%20to%20prompt%20the%20chatbot%20to%20use%20racial%20slurs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20the%20company%20posted%20a%20job%20description%20for%20a%20role%20that%20would%20focus%20on%20%26quot%3Bsafety%20%26amp%3B%20social%20impact%2C%26quot%3B%20calling%20for%20%26quot%3Btalented%20researchers%20and%20engineers%20to%20improve%20the%20safety%20of%20our%20AI%20systems%20and%20ensure%20that%20they%20are%20maximally%20beneficial%20for%20society.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20role%20will%20focus%20on%20%26quot%3Bred%20teaming%20mechanisms%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20job%20posting.%20Red%20teams%2C%20which%20are%20common%20in%20the%20AI%20world%2C%20are%20designed%20to%20prevent%20large%20language%20models%20from%20generating%20illegal%20content%20or%20material%20that%20could%20violate%20user%20policies.%20They%20push%20the%20models%20to%20the%20limit%20to%20find%20use%20cases%20that%20the%20general%20public%20might%20exploit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20xAI%20rival%20OpenAI%20released%20GPT-4%2C%20the%20company%20said%20it%20used%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-gpt4-openai-answer-creepy-dangerous-murder-bomb-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ered%20team%20to%20ask%20questions%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20how%20to%20commit%20murder%2C%20build%20a%20weapon%2C%20or%20use%20racial%20slurs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20xAI%20job%20description%20said%20the%20position%20could%20include%20anything%20from%20working%20to%20counter%20misinformation%20and