ed%20it%20for%2C%20you'll%20typically%20owe%20capital%20gains%20tax%20on%20the%20profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20amount%20depends%20on%20factors%20like%20how%20long%20you%20owned%20the%20property%20and%20your%20taxable%20income%2C%20but%20it%20could%20be%20as%20high%20as%2037%25%20if%20you%20sell%20within%20a%20year%20and%20trigger%20short-term%20capital%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20could%20also%20avoid%20capital%20gains%20tax%20completely.%20CPA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjlkrosenberger.com%2Fexpert%2Fkristel-espinosa-cpa%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKristel%20Espinosa%3C%2Fa%3E%20highlighted%20two%20IRS%20rules%20that%20all%20property%20owners%20looking%20to%20reduce%20their%20tax%20bill%20should%20familiarize%20themselves%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221aeac1d8-952b-4a1d-bade-7ffdaead2b30%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Defer%20taxes%20indefinitely%20with%20a%201031%20exchange%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2F1031-exchange%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1031%20exchange%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Blike-kind%26quot%3B%20exchange%20%E2%80%94%20allows%20investors%20to%20avoid%20capital%20gains%20tax%20if%20they%20swap%20one%20investment%20property%20for%20another%20one%20of%20equal%20or%20higher%20value.%20This%20rule%20is%20specifically%20for%20investment%20properties%2C%20not%20for%20primary%20residences%20or%20vacation%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20way%20to%20defer%20capital%20gains%20by%20reinvesting%20the%20proceeds%20into%20a%20like-kind%20property%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Espinosa%2C%20noting%20that%20this%20strategy%20is%20best%20for%20investors%20who%20plan%20to%20buy%20and%20hold%20real%20estate%20for%20the%20long%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20meant%20for%20people%20who%20just%20want%20to%20purchase%20real%20estate%2C%20flip%20it%20real%20quick%2C%20and%20then%20get%20another%20one.%20The%20whole%20point%20is%20getting%20the%20gain%20to%20be%20deferred%20into%20the%20future%2C%20so%20if%20you're%20constantly%20buying%20and%20selling%20and%20flipping%20properties%2C%20this%201031%20game%20doesn't%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20pay%20capital%20gains%20tax%20when%20you%20sell%20for%20good%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20no%20limit%20to%20the%20number%20of%201031%20exchanges%20you%20do%20%E2%80%94%20but%20you%20can%20theoretically%20avoid%20capital%20gains%20tax%20indefinitely%20if%20you%20continue%20re-investing%20in%20like-kind%20rentals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEspinosa%20said%20her%20clients%20use%20this%20strategy%20to%20diversify%20their%20portfolio%20or%20upgrade%20to%20a%20property%20with%20better%20cash%20flow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20strict%20time%20limit%20on%201031%20exchanges%3A%20You%20must%20identify%20your%20replacement%20property%20(or%20properties)%20in%20writing%20within%2045%20days%20of%20selling%20the%20first%20property.%20Then%20you%20must%20close%20on%20the%20replacement%20property%20within%20180%20days%20of%20your%20initial%20property%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestor%20Zeona%20McIntyre%20told%20BI%20how%20she%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investor-used-1031-exchange-grow-portfolio-avoid-taxes-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eused%20a%201031%20exchange%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20upgrade%20from%20a%20small%2C%20short-term%20rental%20property%20in%20St.%20Louis%20to%20a%20multifamily%20in%20Florida%20that%20produced%20stronger%20cash%20flow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222316%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22zeona%20mcintyre%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f43b183fe8d39283625fae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221737%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZeona%20McIntyre%20is%20a%20real-estate%20investor%20and%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3B30-Day%20Stay.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Zeona%20McIntyre%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%201031%20exchange%20allows%20you%20to%20defer%20your%20tax%20burden%3B%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20think%2C%20'Oh%2C%20I%20don't%20pay%20any%20taxes%2C'%20but%20you're%20technically%20kicking%20the%20can%20down%20the%20road%2C%26quot%3B%20McIntyre%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20cool%20thing%2C%20though%2C%20is%20that%20you%20can%20do%20unlimited%201031%20exchanges%20and%20infinitely%20kick%20it%20down%20the%20road.%20And%20then%20when%20you%20pass%20away%2C%20if%20you%20pass%20that%20on%20to%20someone%20else%2C%20like%20your%20children%20or%20a%20family%20member%2C%20the%20inherited%20home%20does%20not%20have%20the%20tax%20burden%20anymore.%20So%20it%20dies%20with%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20investor%20spoke%20to%20BI%20about%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investor-shares-realities-of-doing-a-1031-exchange-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eattempted%201031%20exchange%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20ultimately%20failed%20because%20of%20the%20tight%20180-day%20timeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20my%20opinion%2C%20that's%20not%20enough%20time.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20rushed%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Steve%20Lewis%2C%20who%20owns%20properties%20in%20New%20Jersey%20and%20ended%20up%20walking%20away%20from%20the%20exchange%20and%20paying%20capital%20gains%20tax%20on%20the%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20major%20takeaway%20was%20that%20180%20days%20go%20by%20faster%20than%20you%20may%20think.%20While%20his%20failed%201031%20experience%20may%20be%20%26quot%3Brare%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere%20are%20so%20many%20things%20that%20could%20delay%20a%20closing.%26quot%3B%20If%20you%20plan%20to%20do%20an%20exchange%2C%20his%20advice%20is%20to%20plan%20ahead%20as%20much%20as%20you%20possibly%20can%20for%20the%20next%20property%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2299566b7e-f27b-40ef-8c3a-6cda30b161db%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Exclude%20up%20to%20%24500%2C000%20of%20the%20gain%20of%20a%20home%20sale%20with%20the%20121%20exclusion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20a%20homeowner%20looking%20to%20sell%2C%20you%20may%20benefit%20from%20the%20Section%20121%20Exclusion%2C%20an%20IRS%20rule%20that%20lets%20taxpayers%20exclude%20up%20to%20%24250%2C000%20of%20the%20gain%20from%20the%20sale.%20A%20couple%20filing%20jointly%20can%20exclude%20up%20to%20%24500%2C000.%20If%20you're%20an%20individual%20and%20sell%20your%20home%20for%20a%20gain%20of%20%24200%2C000%2C%20for%20example%2C%20you%20won't%20have%20to%20pay%20capital%20gains%20tax%20on%20that%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20few%20stipulations%3A%20You%20must%20use%20the%20home%20as%20your%20primary%20residence%20for%20at%20least%20two%20of%20the%20five%20years%20preceding%20the%20sale.%20If%20you're%20selling%20a%20vacation%20home%2C%20for%20example%2C%20you%20can't%20use%20the%20exclusion.%20You%20can%20also%20only%20use%20the%20exclusion%20every%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20rule%20won't%20be%20applicable%20to%20new%20homeowners%2C%20said%20Espinosa%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20good%20option%20for%20people%20who%20have%20been%20in%20their%20primary%20residence%20for%20years%20and%20are%20looking%20to%20sell%20%E2%80%94%20and%20even%20applies%20to%20people%20who%20have%20turned%20their%20primary%20residence%20into%20a%20rental%2C%20as%20long%20as%20they%20satisfy%20the%20two-out-of-five-year%20rule.%20The%20two%20years%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20consecutive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20home%20profits%20more%20than%20%24250%2C000%20as%20an%20individual%20or%20%24500%2C000%20as%20a%20couple%2C%20you'll%20pay%20capital%20gains%20tax%20on%20the%20amount%20that%20exceeds%20the%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22carl%20mindy%20jensen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662994540dfb1341e9feebca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222736%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFinancially%20independent%20couple%20Carl%20and%20Mindy%20Jensen%20built%20wealth%20doing%20live-in%20flips.%3Cp%3ECarl%20and%20Mindy%20Jensen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20couple%20explained%20to%20BI%20how%20they%20used%20the%20exclusion%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-flipping-couple-explain-how-they-avoid-capital-gains-tax-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eavoid%20capital%20gains%20tax%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20each%20of%20their%20property%20sales.%20For%20years%2C%20Carl%20and%20Mindy%20Jensen%20did%20%26quot%3Blive-in%20flips%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20which%20they%20would%20live%20in%20a%20property%20while%20renovating%20it.%20They%20made%20sure%20to%20live%20in%20the%20property%20for%20at%20least%20two%20years%20to%20capitalize%20on%20the%20tax%20rule%20%E2%80%94%20at%20that%20point%2C%20they'd%20sell%2C%20avoid%20capital%20gains%20tax%2C%20and%20start%20their%20next%20live-in%20flip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20used%20the%20exclusion%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20early%202000s%20when%20they%20bought%20a%20home%20for%20%24135%2C000%2C%20upgraded%20the%20carpet%2C%20walls%2C%20and%20bathrooms%2C%20and%20sold%20it%20for%20%24235%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20we%20lived%20in%20it%20and%20owned%20it%20for%20two%20of%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20we%20paid%20no%20taxes%20on%20the%20capital%20gains%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mindy.%20While%20their%20gains%20were%20around%20%24100%2C000%2C%20they%20could%20have%20excluded%20up%20to%20%24500%2C000%20since%20they%20were%20both%20on%20the%20title.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20we%20did%20it%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20bought%20another%20house%20for%20%24265%2C00%20and%20sold%20it%20for%20%24365%2C000%2C%20so%20we%20made%20another%20100%2C000.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20the%20IRS%20rule%2C%20that%20%24100%2C000%20was%20also%20shielded%20from%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Favoid-capital-gains-tax-on-sale-of-home-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744188302000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f437d7c6ad288d147d7592%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Favoid-capital-gains-tax-on-sale-of-home-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Section%20121%20Exclusion%20lets%20taxpayers%20exclude%20up%20to%20%24250%2C000%20of%20the%20gain%20from%20the%20sale.%20A%20couple%20filing%20jointly%20can%20exclude%20up%20to%20%24500%2C000.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kelkins%40businessinsider.com%20(Kathleen%20Elkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Favoid-capital-gains-tax-on-sale-of-home-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20much%20iPhone%20prices%20might%20rise%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20and%20when%20it%20could%20happen%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22iPhones%20in%20a%20line%2C%20different%20colors%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f528c13fe8d39283626cc9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20analysts%20predict%20some%20iPhone%20models%20will%20increase%20in%20price%20by%20%24350.%3Cp%3EMichael%20M.%20Santiago%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20analysts%20predict%20Apple%20could%20hike%20iPhone%20prices%20by%20up%20to%20%24350%20because%20of%20new%20tariffs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple's%3C%2Fa%3E%20costs%20are%20expected%20to%20go%20up%20roughly%2030%25%20to%2050%25%20from%20tariffs%2C%20analysts%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EApple%20will%20try%20to%20negotiate%20with%20Trump%20and%20suppliers%20to%20avoid%20passing%20on%20the%20full%20costs%20to%20consumers%2C%20analysts%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump's%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20tariff%20announcement%20sent%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericans-worried-tariffs-stock-up-essentials-cut-back-luxuries-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsumers%20rushing%20to%20upgrade%3C%2Fa%3E%20their%20iPhones%20because%20they%20were%20afraid%20of%20price%20increases.%20But%20how%20much%20more%20could%20you%20end%20up%20paying%20for%20a%20new%20iPhone%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmarketer%20analyst%20Jacob%20Bourne%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20iPhones%20and%20other%20Apple%20devices%20could%20go%20up%20%26quot%3Bhundreds%20of%20dollars.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20White%20House%20announcing%20plans%20to%20implement%20a%20total%20tariff%20rate%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-liberation-day-reciprocal-tariffs-speech-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E104%25%20on%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20BI%20spoke%20to%20seven%20analysts%20about%20what%20consumers%20can%20expect%20in%20terms%20of%20price%20hikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222ecbfbe2-d87d-4d6d-a354-6db2f535096e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEstimated%20price%20increases%20of%2030%25%20to%2040%25%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20blog%20post%20outlining%20how%20some%20tech%20products%20will%20be%20impacted%20by%20tariffs%2C%20UBS's%20Chief%20Investment%20Office%20wrote%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fiphone-16%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiPhone%2016%3C%2Fa%3E%20Pro%20Max%20with%20256%20GB%2C%20which%20is%20assembled%20in%20Mainland%20China%2C%20will%20likely%20see%20a%20price%20hike%20of%20%24350%20%E2%80%94%20bringing%20its%20price%20tag%20up%20to%20%241%2C549.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-iphone-mac-products-great-classic-boring-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20likely%20to%20see%20the%20same%20price%20increases.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20iPhone%2016%20Pro%20with%20128%20GB%20is%20assembled%20in%20India%2C%20which%20is%20set%20to%20have%20a%20total%2026%25%20tariff%20rate%20that%20goes%20into%20effect%20on%20Wednesday.%20That%20model%20is%20expected%20to%20increase%20by%2012%25%2C%20which%20would%20be%20%24120%2C%20UBS%20wrote%20in%20the%20blog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUBS%20wrote%20that%20it's%20%26quot%3Bnear%20impossible%26quot%3B%20to%20come%20up%20with%20exact%20figures%20on%20price%20increases%2C%20and%20it's%20also%20unclear%20how%20much%20the%20iPhone%20company%20will%20end%20up%20passing%20on%20to%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBourne%20told%20BI%20that%20if%20consumers%20are%20grappling%20with%20tariffs%20on%20other%20goods%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericans-worried-tariffs-stock-up-essentials-cut-back-luxuries-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20also%20possibly%20dealing%20with%20a%20market%20crisis%2C%20they%20%26quot%3Baren't%20going%20to%20want%20to%20pay%26quot%3B%20for%20that%20kind%20of%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsumers%20really%20have%20to%20look%20at%20their%20bandwidth%20for%20discretionary%20expenses%20and%20certainly%20Apple's%20products%2C%20including%20the%20iPhone%2C%20can%20be%20a%20big%20ticket%20item%2C%26quot%3B%20Bourne%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThomas%20Monteiro%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FInvesting.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInvesting.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20that%20if%20Apple%20ends%20up%20passing%20on%20the%20costs%20to%20consumers%2C%20companies%20like%20Samsung%2C%20which%20are%20less%20impacted%20by%20tariffs%2C%20could%20gain%20a%20competitive%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20IHT%20Wealth%20Management%20chief%20investment%20officer%20Yussef%20Gheriani%20told%20BI%20that%20%26quot%3Bcustomers%20are%20too%20entrenched%20in%20their%20ecosystem%20to%20easily%20break%20from%20the%20brand.%26quot%3B%20Gheriani%20said%20he%20expects%20%26quot%3Ba%20majority%20if%20not%20all%20of%20the%20cost%20increases%26quot%3B%20that%20Apple%20endures%20to%20be%20passed%20on%20to%20consumers%2C%20although%20it's%20possible%20telecom%20companies%20could%20take%20on%20some%20of%20the%20costs%2C%20or%20that%20financing%20Apple%20purchases%20becomes%20more%20common.%20That%20could%20make%20price%20increases%20%26quot%3Beasier%20to%20swallow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cd150a55-64de-4395-bb63-0207fd15e143%5C%22%3EWhy%20Apple%20may%20be%20able%20to%20get%20away%20with%20price%20hikes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDipanjan%20Chatterjee%2C%20vice%20president%20and%20principal%20analyst%20at%20Forrester%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20Apple%20can%20probably%20increase%20prices%20for%20some%20of%20its%20products%2C%20like%20the%20iPhone%2C%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20significant%20detriment%2C%26quot%3B%20even%20if%20it%20has%20high%20margins%20and%20could%20afford%20to%20absorb%20some%20of%20the%20costs%20of%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChatterjee%20said%20many%20people%20have%20their%20lives%20%26quot%3Bentangled%26quot%3B%20with%20Apple%20platforms%20and%20might%20not%20want%20to%20switch%20to%20a%20new%20brand.%20He%20said%20that%20people%20change%20their%20iPhones%20every%20year%20or%20two%20and%20line%20up%20the%20night%20before%20product%20launches%20to%20get%20the%20latest%20version%20of%20something%20that%20isn't%20much%20different%20from%20what%20other%20brands%20are%20offering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20do%20that%20because%20it's%20Apple%2C%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20Chatterjee%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20something%20about%20the%20brand%20that%20demands%20even%20now%20a%20degree%20of%20sort%20of%20fanaticism%20and%20loyalty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2274ac2fcb-0d49-47a4-9a21-a3a52bded33a%5C%22%3EApple%20will%20try%20to%20strike%20a%20deal%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChatterjee%20told%20BI%20that%20Apple%20could%20try%20a%20more%20long-term%20approach%20of%20moving%20its%20manufacturing%20to%20the%20US%20or%20move%20production%20from%20high-tariff%20countries%20to%20lower-tariff%20countries.%20Apple%20has%20already%20reportedly%20tried%20to%20do%20so%2C%20with%20plans%20underway%20to%20source%20more%20iPhones%20from%20India%2C%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Ftech%2Fapple-iphone-production-china-tariffs-6cc37f40%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20short%20term%20though%2C%20all%20of%20the%20analysts%20BI%20spoke%20to%20agreed%20that%20Apple%20will%20try%20to%20avoid%20the%20extra%20costs%20by%20negotiating%20a%20deal%20either%20with%20the%20Trump%20Administration%20or%20the%20suppliers%20it%20works%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wouldn't%20be%20the%20first%20time%20Apple%20tried%20to%20cut%20a%20deal%20under%20pressure.%20The%20tech%20giant%20is%20known%20to%20take%20on%20an%20assertive%20approach%20in%20its%20negotiations%2C%20and%20it's%20been%20successful%20in%20many%20instances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20kind%20of%20their%20lobbying%20apparatus%20that%20kicks%20in%20and%20tries%20to%20convince%20the%20administration%20for%20whatever%20reason%20they%20should%20not%20be%20subject%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Chaterjee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20previously%20praised%20Apple%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftim-cook%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETim%20Cook%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20his%20dealmaking%20approach.%20Trump%20said%20that%20during%20his%20first-term%2C%20Cook%20reached%20out%20to%20him%20when%20a%2025%25%20and%2050%25%20tariff%20would%20impact%20Apple%20products%20imported%20from%20China.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-praises-tim-cook-describes-private-meeting-when-president-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo%20ended%20up%20making%20a%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Trump%20would%20back%20down%20from%20the%20tariffs%20if%20Apple%20manufactured%20more%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225b63b8c4-3727-44ca-bac7-1e5be25ba2d1%5C%22%3EThe%20sooner%2C%20the%20better%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20Apple%20can't%20dodge%20the%20tariffs%20this%20time%20around%2C%20price%20hikes%20to%20its%20products%20likely%20won't%20happen%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmarketer%20analyst%20Bourne%20said%20that%20Apple%20could%20potentially%20get%20by%20on%20months%20on%20emergency%20shipments%20of%20iPhones%20that%20it%20flew%20in%20ahead%20of%20tariffs%20to%20avoid%20some%20of%20the%20impact.%20Willcox%2C%20from%20Consumer%20Reports%2C%20said%20pricing%20will%20also%20depend%20on%20how%20much%20inventory%20Apple%20has%2C%20and%20how%20fast%20it%20ends%20up%20selling%20it.%20In%20the%20last%20week%20of%20March%2C%20the%20tech%20giant%20reportedly%20transported%20five%20planes%20of%20iPhones%20and%20other%20products%20from%20India%20to%20the%20US%2C%20The%20Times%20of%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Fmobiles-tabs%2Fhow-apple-flew-5-flights-full-of-iphones-from-india-and-china-in-3-days-to-beat-trump-tariffs%2Farticleshow%2F120044321.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBourne%20said%20if%20a%20buyer%20has%20less%20urgency%20for%20a%20new%20iPhone%2C%20they%20could%20hedge%20their%20bets%20and%20hold%20off%20on%20a%20purchase%20until%20tariffs%20and%20negotiations%20are%20finalized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20if%20you%20know%20you'll%20need%20a%20new%20iPhone%20soon%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20bad%20idea%20to%20act%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECraig%20Moffett%2C%20senior%20analyst%20at%20MoffettNathanson%20told%20BI%20that%20Apple%20isn't%20expected%20to%20drop%20anything%20%26quot%3BEarth%20shaking%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20iPhone%2017.%20So%20buyers%20%26quot%3Bmight%20as%20well%20jump%20now%20to%20get%20ahead%20of%20any%20price%20increase%20risk.%26quot%3B%20Plus%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20bad%20time%20to%20lock%20in%20a%20phone%20deal%2C%20Moffett%20said%2C%20with%20Verizon%20offering%20a%20free%20phone%20deal%20and%20three%20year%20price%20guarantee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fiphone-prices-trump-tariff-impact-cost-timeline-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744188001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f528f8a466d2b74ab28615%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fiphone-prices-trump-tariff-impact-cost-timeline-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Analysts%20predict%20Apple's%20costs%20will%20increase%20by%20roughly%2030%25%20to%2050%25%20with%20tariffs%2C%20leading%20some%20iPhone%20models%20to%20go%20up%20as%20much%20as%20%24350.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aaltchek%40insider.com%20(Ana%20Altchek)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A173%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fiphone-prices-trump-tariff-impact-cost-timeline-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Taking%20Electricity%2C%20Wherever%20They%20Go%3A%20Engineer%E2%80%99s%20Portable%20Solar%20Units%20Power%20Huts%20of%20Tribal%20Migrants%20in%20Maharashtra%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EImagine%20a%20life%20where%20night%20descends%20as%20an%20impenetrable%20blackness%2C%20electricity%20is%20a%20lush%20distant%20dream%2C%20and%20safety%20is%20a%20constant%20battle.%20This%20was%20the%20reality%20for%20the%20Katkari%20and%20Kunbi%20tribal%20commu