20main%20issue%20is%20that%20it%20looks%20wrong%20next%20to%20the%20temple.%20I%20can't%20understand%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20then%20shows%20a%20man%20asking%20a%20customer%20about%20%26quot%3Bjeevhatya%26quot%3B%20--%20meaning%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20living%20being%20--%20next%20to%20the%20temple%2C%20which%20also%20has%20an%20idol%20of%20Lord%20Hanuman.%20The%20customer%20responds%20that%20animal%20practice%20is%20common%20in%20many%20temples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%20shared%20the%20video%20and%20accused%20%26quot%3BBJP%20goons%26quot%3B%20of%20threatening%20fish-eating%20Bengalis.%20%26quot%3BNever%20in%2060%20years%20has%20this%20happened%2C%20residents%20say%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%20She%20added%20that%20this%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bpresent%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20three-month-old%20BJP%20government%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThese%20fish%20shops%20were%20allotted%20by%20DDA%2C%20this%20is%20not%20any%20illegal%20encroachment.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIf%20BJP%20had%20problem%20with%20CR%20Park%20Bengalis%20eating%20fish%2C%20they%20should%20have%20said%20so%20in%20their%20manifesto.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnBengalis%20in%20CR%20Park%20are%20one%20of%20the%20most%20educated%20communities%20in%20Delhi.%20Their%20sentiments%20and%20eating%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FoRv2S8bHfi%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FoRv2S8bHfi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20(%40Saurabh_MLAgk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSaurabh_MLAgk%2Fstatus%2F1909619928204034268%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%208%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20Ms%20Moitra%20post%2C%20former%20Delhi%20minister%20and%20AAP%20leader%20Saurabh%20Bhardwaj%20said%20the%20DDA%20had%20allotted%20the%20fis