0it%20today.%20A%20couple%20of%20your%20congressmen%20said%2C%20'I%20think%20we%20should%20get%20involved%20in%20the%20negotiation%20of%20the%20tariffs%2C%20'%26quot%3B%20he%20mocked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20said%20that%20Congress's%20negotiations%20would%20make%20China%20the%20happiest%2C%20as%20China%20would%20not%20have%20to%20pay%20any%20tariffs%3B%20the%20US%20would%20pay%20them%20instead!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOh%2C%20that's%20what%20I%20need-%20I%20need%20some%20guy%20telling%20me%20how%20to%20negotiate.%20I%20tell%20you%2C%20the%20happiest%20people%20in%20the%20world%20would%20be%20Chinese.%20They%20wouldn't%20be%20paying%20104%20per%20cent.%20I%20tell%2C%20they'd%20be%20paying%20no%20per%20cent%20%5Binstead%5D%20we'd%20be%20paying%20them%20104%20per%20cent%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20also%20said%20that%20he%20would%20announce%20major%20tariffs%20on%20the%20pharma%20sector%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTariffs%20on%20pharma%20will%20be%20there%20because%20we%20don't%20make%20our%20own%20pharma%20drugs%3B%20they%20are%20made%20in%20another%20country.%20The%20same%20packet%20in%20the%20US%20is%20priced%20at%20USD%2010%20or%20more.%20We%20are%20going%20to%20tariff%20pharma%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20companies%20will%20come%20rushing%20to%20us%20very%20soon.%20The%20advantage%20we%20have%20is%2C%20we%20are%20very%20big%20market.%20Very%20shortly%2C%20will%20announce%20a%20major%20tariff%20on%20pharma%2C%20and%20when%20these%20companies%20hear%20that%2C%20they%20will%20leave%20China%20and%20other%20countries%20because%20most%20of%20their%20products%20are%20sold%20here.%20And%2C%20they%20will%20be%20opening%20their%20plants%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744178820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3