3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Freserve-bank-of-india-cuts-key-lending-rate-by-25-basis-points-to-6-as-trump-tariffs-kick-in-8121755%5C%22%3Erepo%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20interest%20rate%20at%20which%20the%20RBI%20lends%20money%20to%20commercial%20banks%20for%20short-term%20needs%2C%20usually%20against%20government%20securities.%20It's%20a%20key%20tool%20used%20by%20the%20central%20bank%20to%20manage%20inflation%20and%20liquidity%20in%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Did%20The%20RBI%20Cut%20The%20Repo%20Rate%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20reduces%20the%20repo%20rate%20when%20it%20wants%20to%20inject%20more%20liquidity%20into%20the%20system%20and%20boost%20economic%20activity%20-%20especially%20when%20inflation%20is%20under%20control.%20For%20FY26%2C%20the%20RBI%20has%20projected%20Consumer%20Price%20Index%20(CPI)%20inflation%20at%204%25%2C%20comfortably%20within%20its%20target%20range%20of%202-6%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGlobal%20uncertainties%20over%20trade%20tensions%20triggered%20by%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20have%20also%20influenced%20the%20decision%2C%20as%20they%20pose%20risks%20to%20global%20growth%20and%20India's%20exports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Will%20It%20Affect%20You%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELoan%20EMIs%20May%20Get%20Cheaper%20-%20With%20the%20repo%20rate%20cut%2C%20banks%20and%20financial%20institutions%20can%20borrow%20funds%20from%20the%20RBI%20at%20a%20lower%20cost.%20This%20could%20lower%20interest%20rates%20on%20home%20loans%2C%20auto%20loans%2C%20and%20new%20personal%20loans.%20The%20actual%20reduction%20in%20EMIs%2C%20however%2C%20depends%20on%20how%20quickly%20and%20to%20what%20extent%20individual%20banks%20pass%20on%20the%20benefits%20to%20consumers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EImpact%20On%20Fixed%20Deposits%20-%20While%20borrowers%20may%20cheer%2C%20fixed%20deposit%20(FD)%20investors%20could%20see%20a%20downside.%20As%20lending%20rates%20go%20down%2C%20banks%20may%20also%20cut%20interest%20rates%20on%20deposits%20to%20protect%20their%20margins.%20New%20FD%20investors%20might%20earn%20lower%20returns%20than%20those%20who%20locked%20in%20earlier%20at%20higher%20rates.%20If%20you%20are%20planning%20to%20invest%20in%20FDs%2C%20it%20might%20be%20wise%20to%20do%20so%20before%20banks%20revise%20rates%20downward.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPersonal%20Loan%20Borrowers%20-%20If%20you%20already%20have%20a%20personal%20loan%2C%20especially%20one%20with%20a%20fixed%20interest%20rate%2C%20your%20EMI%20will%20likely%20remain%20the%20same.%20But%20if%20you%20are%20planning%20to%20take%20a%20new%20personal%20loan%2C%20the%20rate%20cut%20could%20mean%20lower%20interest%20rates%20and%20more%20affordable%20repayments.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernor%20Sanjay%20Malhotra%20said%20the%20Indian%20economy%20was%20on%20track%2C%20projecting%20GDP%20growth%20at%206.5%25%20for%20FY%202025-26.%20This%20is%20the%20quarterly%20breakdown%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EQ1%3A%206.5%25%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EQ2%3A%206.7%25%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EQ3%3A%206.6%25%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EQ4%3A%206.3%25%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20the%20agriculture%20sector%20looks%20promising%20due%20to%20healthy%20reservoir%20levels%20and%20robust%20crop%20production.%20The%20manufacturing%20and%20services%20sectors%20are%20showing%20signs%20of%20revival%2C%20and%20urban%20consumption%20is%20gradually%20picking%20up.%20Investment%20activity%20is%20rising%2C%20backed%20by%20strong%20corporate%20and%20bank%20balance%20sheets%20and%20continued%20government%20focus%20on%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744177620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F1ok4u97o_home-loan_625x300_07_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Frbi-cuts-repo-rate-for-2nd-