p%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20deliberate%20and%20decide%20on%20the%20policy%20reparations%2C%20the%20global%20economic%20outlook%20is%20fast%20changing.%20The%20recent%20trade%20tariff-related%20measures%20have%20exacerbated%20uncertainties%2C%20clouding%20the%20economic%20outlook%20across%20regions%2C%20posing%20new%20headwinds%20for%20global%20growth%20and%20inflation.%20Amidst%20this%20turbulence%2C%20the%20US%20dollar%20has%20weakened%20appreciably%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20while%20global%20trade%20and%20policy%20uncertainties%20will%20impede%20growth%2C%20there%20is%20no%20concern%20about%20managing%20domestic%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20announcements%2C%20the%20central%20bank%20said%20the%20repo%20rate%20will%20be%20cut%20by%2025%20basis%20points%20to%206%20per%20cent.%C2%A0This%20marks%20the%20second%20consecutive%20rate%20cut%20in%20recent%20months.%20On%20February%207%2C%20the%20central%20bank%20had%20reduced%20the%20repo%20rate%20from%206.5%20per%20cent%20to%206.25%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcements%20came%20after%20Trump's%20punishing%20tariffs%20on%20dozens%20of%20economies%20came%20in%20force%2C%20including%20over%20100%20per%20cent%20in%20levies%20against%20Chinese%20goods%2C%20dramatically%20ramping%20up%20a%20devastating%20global%20trade%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20said%20the%20United%20States%20was%20%26quot%3Btaking%20in%20almost%20%242%20billion%20a%20day%26quot%3B%20from%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBenchmark%20equity%20indices%20slumped%20in%20early%20trade%20after%20a%20day's%20breather%20in%20line%20with%20losses%20in%20Asian%20markets%20amid%20escalating%20trade%20tensions.%C2%A0The%2030-share%20BSE%20benchmark%20Sensex%20dropped%20554.02%20points%20to%2073%2C673.06%20in%20early%20trade.%20The%20NSE%20Nifty%20declined%20178.85%20points%20to%2022%2C357.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Asian%20markets%2C%20Tokyo's%20Nikkei%20225%20index%2C%20South%20Korea's%20Kospi%20