ecognising%20an%20opportunity%2C%20Shraddha%20started%20posting%20tutorials.%20By%20the%20time%20she%20was%2016%2C%20her%20follower%20base%20had%20grown%20to%20a%20staggering%201.75%20million.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20social%20media%20success%20became%20her%20financial%20backing%2C%20and%20brand%20deals%20covered%20her%20tournament%20fees.%20As%20her%20fame%20grew%2C%20her%20talent%20caught%20the%20eye%20of%20Piyush%20Kumar%2C%20the%20co-founder%20of%20ART%20Talent%20Management.%20Through%20his%20firm%2C%20Piyush%20helped%20Shraddha%20secure%20brand%20collaborations%20and%20took%20care%20of%20her%20social%20media%20posts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20looking%20for%20talents%20that%20require%20support%20to%20flourish%20in%20their%20domains%20and%20stumbled%20upon%20Shraddha%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Piyush.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20road%20to%20medals%20and%20milestones%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShraddha%E2%80%99s%20competitive%20journey%20reached%20new%20heights%20in%202023%20when%20she%20entered%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F32273%2Fmohammad-iftekhar-khan-in-kickboxing-nationals%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Kickboxing%20Championship%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20first%20time%20and%20secured%20two%20gold%20medals.%20This%20momentum%20carried%20her%20into%202024%2C%20a%20year%20packed%20with%20international%20challenges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFacing%20a%20demanding%20schedule%2C%20with%20the%20WAKO%20World%20Cup%20before%20the%20Asian%20Kickboxing%20Championship%202024%2C%20she%20had%20virtually%20no%20time%20for%20specific%20preparation.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20performances%20I%20was%20giving%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20and%20Asian%20Championships%20were%20the%20same%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%20With%20two%20major%20events%20on%20the%20horizon%20and%20only%20three%20months%20to%20prepare%2C%20she%20dedicated%20herself%20to%