%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20occasionally%20train%20with%20Shraddha%20when%20she%20has%20an%20event%20coming%20up%20and%20when%20she%20requires%20a%20fight%20partner%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Ritij%20Rajput%2C%20a%20taekwondo%20athlete%20turned%20bodybuilder.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20fact%20that%20she%20creates%20her%20schedule%20and%20trains%20with%20determination%20is%20the%20reason%20for%20her%20success%20in%20the%20sport%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ritij%20adds%2C%20who%20has%20seen%20her%20taekwondo%20and%20kickboxing%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOvercoming%20the%20formidable%20competition%20requires%20%E2%80%9Cunwavering%20dedication%2C%20visualisation%2C%20training%2C%20and%20manifestation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CI%20only%20have%20one%20mantra%3A%20when%20there%20is%20a%20tournament%2C%20I%20look%20at%20the%20venue%20and%20picture%20it%20in%20my%20mind.%20I%20visualise%20myself%20in%20the%20venue%20and%20practice%20my%20routine%20again%20and%20again.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20her%20World%20Cup%20experience%20left%20her%20slightly%20dissatisfied%2C%20with%20one%20gold%20and%20three%20silver%20medals%2C%20her%20performance%20at%20the%20Asian%20Championships%20exceeded%20expectations.%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20expect%20to%20win%20two%20gold%20medals%20and%20two%20silvers%20since%20there%20were%20leading%20countries%20like%20China%2C%20Philippines%2C%20Thailand%2C%20and%20Indonesia%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20admits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T160421.362-1744022073.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shraddha%20winning%20an%20event%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T160421.362-1744022073.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-me