ickboxing%20is%20no%20exception%20when%20it%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F186108%2Findia-muay-thai-richa-gaur-female-athlete-fighting-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomes%20to%20gender%20inequality%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20understood%20that%20wherever%20you%20go%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20be%20judged%20for%20being%20a%20woman%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shraddha%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CStatements%20like%20%E2%80%98running%20and%20standing%20like%20a%20girl%E2%80%99%20made%20me%20wonder%20if%20I%20needed%20to%20be%20ashamed%20for%20being%20a%20girl.%20I%20wanted%20to%20change%20this%20narrative%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Shraddha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20response%20is%20to%20challenge%20these%20stereotypes%20head-on.%20%E2%80%9CI%20fight%20with%20boys%20and%20defeat%20them%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20states.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20now%20I%20get%20a%20new%20comment%20saying%20%E2%80%98I%20fight%20like%20a%20boy.%E2%80%99%20Just%20because%20I%20am%20stronger%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20I%20have%20to%20change%20my%20gender%2C%20right%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20experiences%20were%20initially%20frustrating%2C%20they%20now%20evoke%20a%20deeper%20sense%20of%20sadness.%20%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20sad%20when%20people%20link%20strength%20with%20gender%20when%20the%20former%20comes%20from%20consistent%20training%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20golden%20dream%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShraddha%E2%80%99s%20gaze%20is%20firmly%20fixed%20on%20the%20future%2C%20defined%20by%20a%20series%20of%20ambitious%20short-term%20goals.%20With%20the%20Italian%20World%20Cup%20in%20March%20and%20subsequent%20tournaments%20in%20Thailand%2C%20Turkey%2C%20and%20Uzbekistan%2C%20her%20schedule%20is%20packed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20ultimate%20dream%20lies%20in%20the%202025%20World%20Championship.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20main%20focus%20is%20on%20