0green%20energy%20initiative%2C%20makes%20this%20possible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDarewadi%E2%80%99s%20transformation%20is%20fascinating.%20And%20Kalki%20Vundamati%2C%20consultant%20at%20Gram%20Oorja%2C%20beckons%20your%20attention%20to%20the%20150%20other%20villages%20that%20mirror%20the%20same%20success.%20As%20of%202025%2C%20the%20initiative%20has%20installed%20152%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F161052%2Fiisc-maharashtra-innovation-ghana-bolivia%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20microgrids%3C%2Fa%3E%20thus%20electrifying%20over%206%2C200%20households%20in%20remote%20off-grid%20villages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsolar-3_11zon-1743772299.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Villages%20across%20India%20that%20previously%20were%20reliant%20on%20traditional%20grids%20are%20now%20harnessing%20the%20power%20of%20the%20Sun%20and%20earning%20through%20it%20too%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsolar-3_11zon-1743772299.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsolar-3_11zon-1743772299-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsolar-3_11zon-1743772299-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsolar-3_11zon-1743772299-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsolar-3_11zon-1743772299-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-418046%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVillages%20across%20India%20that%20previously%20were%20reliant%20on%20traditional%20grids%20are%20now%20harnessing%20the%20power%20of%20the%20Sun%20and%20earning%20through%20it%20too%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Gram%20Oorja%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20770%20solar%20pumping%20based%20group%20irrigation%20systems%20have%20helped%20over%203%2C400%20farming%20families%20farm%20beyond%20the%20monsoon%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kalki%20adds.%20With%20over%2016%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20equipping%20villages%20with%20sustainable%20and%20community-driven%20energy%20solutions%2C%20Gram%20Oorja%20brings%20a%20well-groomed%20gaze%20to%20the%20debate%20of%20solar%20microgrids.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20success%20lies%20in%20its%20model.%20Villages%20are%20earmarked%20for%20solar%20adoption%20following%20a%20comprehensive%20survey%20and%20community%20engagement%20exercises%2C%20after%20which%20need-based%20systems%20are%20designed.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352853%2Fgadge-meenakshi-mukhra-ecovillage-telangana-solar-power-plantation-drives%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evillage%E2%80%99s%20ability%20and%20willingness%20to%20adopt%20new%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20assessed%2C%20followed%20by%20intense%20community%20interactions%2C%20which%20gauge%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20ability%20and%20willingness%20to%20pay%20metered%20bills.%20The%20final%20step%20is%20ownership%20transfer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20ensures%20that%20solar%20adoption%20is%20not%20a%20fleeting%20inclusion%2C%20but%20instead%20sustainable.%20Monthly%20tariff%20collections%20through%20a%20village%20committee%20bank%20account%20pin%20accountability%20on%20the%20locals.%20And%20the%20model%E2%80%99s%20success%20is%20measured%20by%20a%20recent%20study%20that%20Gram%20Oorja%20conducted%2C%20where%2074%20percent%20of%20villagers%20felt%20proud%20about%20the%20solar%20installations%20being%20managed%20entirely%20by%20community%20members.%20They%20shared%20how%20it%20furthered%20their%20intent%20to%20help%20in%20the%20upkeep.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20villages%20of%20India%2C%20this%20model%20%E2%80%94%20of%20putting%20the%20onus%20of%20solar%20adoption%20and%20upkeep%20on%20the%20locals%20%E2%80%94%20is%20tasting%20success.%20Take%20for%20instance%20the%20%E2%80%98Bolega%20Bihar%E2%80%99%20campaign%20(2020)%20that%20pushed%20household-level%20adoption%20of%20decentralised%20renewable%20energy%20solutions%20in%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Gaya%20and%20Nalanda%2C%20and%20saw%20over%20700%20women%20leaders%20become%20stakeholders%20in%20the%20cause%2C%20joining%20in%20solar-related%20discussions.%20In%20another%20successful%20example%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F268152%2Fmaharashtra-village-manyachiwadi-solar-gram-electricity-sustainable-women-success%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Manyachiwadi%20village%20%3C%2Fa%3Eadvocates%20for%20a%20similar%20model.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20village%20set%20a%20precedent%20becoming%20the%20first%20in%20Maharashtra%20to%20be%20100%20percent%20electrified%20by%20solar.%20Almost%20two%20decades%20ago%2C%20when%20conventional%20energy%20was%20reigning%20the%20scene%2C%20Manyachiwadi%20subverted%20the%20trend%20by%20transitioning%20to%20solar.%20They%20started%20small.%20The%20women%20of%20the%20village%20began%20pooling%20in%20Rs%20100%20every%20month%20until%20the%20sum%20was%20enough%20to%20install%20solar%20systems%20in%20their%20homes.%20Today%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20pay%20a%20rupee%20for%20electricity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20world%20beyond%20the%20panels%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERooftop%20solar%20and%20microgrids%20are%20fantastic.%20But%2C%20while%20advocating%20for%20these%2C%20entrepreneurs%20see%20potential%20in%20solar%20devices%20such%20as%20solar%20dryers%2C%20biogas%20grids%20and%20water%20pumps.%20These%20are%20a%20great%20way%20to%20ease%20villages%20into%20the%20world%20of%20renewable%20energy.%20And%20once%20they%20see%20how%20lucrative%20solar%20is%2C%20it%20might%20convince%20them%20to%20invest%20in%20panels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELatika%20Patil%20from%20Dahanu%2C%20Maharashtra%20is%20one%20example.%20She%20belongs%20to%20a%20family%20that%20has%20been%20cultivating%20chickoo%20for%20around%2050%20years.%20But%20the%20harvest%20would%20spoil%20when%20there%20weren%E2%80%99t%20as%20many%20buyers.%20After%20her%20retirement%20in%202015%2C%20Latika%20took%20a%20keen%20interest%20in%20the%20processing%20of%20fruits.%20At%20first%2C%20she%20resorted%20to%20sun-drying%20them%20but%20soon%20stumbled%20upon%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F282854%2Fmaharashtra-family-solar-drying-machine-food-processing-chikoo-increases-sales%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20conduction%20dryer%20(SCD)%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20latter%20was%20more%20favourable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsolar-4-1743772472.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Solar%20conduction%20dryers%20are%20incredibly%20beneficial%20in%20fruit%20processing%20and%20result%20in%20greater%20turnover%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsolar-4-1743772472.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsolar-4-1743772472-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsolar-4-1743772472-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsolar-4-1743772472-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsolar-4-1743772472-150x79.