Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%20from%20hospitals%20across%20India%2C%20between%202020%20and%202023%2C%2050%25%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fvideo%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-heart-attacks-2%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheart%20attack%20patients%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewere%20below%20the%20age%20of%2040.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Sudhakar%20Rao%20M%2C%20Consultant%20Cardiologist%20at%20Manipal%20Hospital%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20confirms%20this%20worrying%20pattern.%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20heart%20attacks%20were%20traditionally%20seen%20in%20people%20beyond%2050%20or%2060.%20But%20in%20the%20last%20two%20decades%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20it%20become%20very%20common%20among%20young%20adults%2C%20particularly%20those%20under%2045.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20are%20young%20people%20at%20risk%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20causes%20of%20heart%20disease%20are%20multifactorial%20%E2%80%94%20with%20genetic%20predisposition%2C%20lifestyle%20choices%2C%20and%20environmental%20factors%20%E2%80%94%20all%20playing%20a%20role.%20While%20some%20risk%20factors%2C%20such%20as%20family%20history%2C%20are%20unavoidable%2C%20many%20others%20can%20be%20managed%20or%20prevented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20most%20significant%20contributors%20is%20smoking%2C%20including%20both%20active%20and%20passive%20smoking.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20used%20to%20think%